bilingual.source: Indoor pond and garden. Calgary, Alberta, Canada.
bilingual.target: 室内的池堂和花园。加拿大卡尔加里。

bilingual.source: Fix the protectors on the indoor walls or windows.
bilingual.target: 将保护器固定在室内的墙壁上.

bilingual.source: Allow plenty of fresh air into the indoor environment.
The outdoor swimming pool is hotter than the indoor one.
bilingual.target: 露天游泳池比室内的热.

bilingual.source: Before work should open ventilation equipment, open indoor door window maintain indoor ventilation.
bilingual.target: 工作前应开启通风设备，打开室内的门窗保持室内通风良好。

bilingual.source: According to the indoor circumstance, shade tolerance and ornament of plants, the indoor application of green plants was discussed.
bilingual.target: 本文主要从室内环境特点、植物的耐荫性、观赏性探讨绿色植物在室内的应用；

bilingual.source: Heated indoor air also can cause your skin to lose moisture during wintertime.
bilingual.target: 冬天，室内的热空气容易将皮肤表面的水份蒸发，皮肤变得比较干燥。

bilingual.source: You can control indoor temperature with the remote controller of the air conditioner too.
bilingual.target: 您也可以用空调遥控器控制室内的温度。

bilingual.source: An outdoor basketball court and indoor ping-pong table offer opportunities for recreation.
bilingual.target: 一个罗田的足球场和一个室内的乒乓球桌为消遣娱乐提供了机会和场所。

bilingual.source: LED festoon lamp--as a low-power light, indoor use only, suited for the ceiling, wall.
bilingual.target: LED双尖灯，属低压灯，适合于室内的墙壁，天花板。

yingyinNormal.en: Sorry. You just seem like, you know, kind of an indoor girl.
yingyinNormal.zh: 抱歉，你看来比较少到户外的大小姐。

yingyinNormal.en: But if you really want to cool down, take the chairlift to the top of the indoor mountain at Ski Dubai.
yingyinNormal.zh: 假如您想要真正清凉感受，可以乘搭缆车到迪拜室内滑雪场的山顶。

yingyinNormal.en: This ski resort in the desert, features five ski runs, including the world's first indoor black diamond slope.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个沙漠上的滑雪渡假村设有5种滑道，包括全球第一条室内黑钻雪道。

yingyinNormal.en: Tropical Hilo is one of the wettest cities in the US, but the many indoor attractions on this part of the east coast will keep you entertained when the heavens open.
yingyinNormal.zh: 热带地区希洛是美国最潮湿的城市之一，但在这里的东岸有许多室内景点会让您流连忘返。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, while Cory and Topanga are checking us in, let me welcome you all to Mount Sun Lodge, where we are here to turn our thoughts away from our indoor relationships and towards our relationships with the outdoors.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好了，现在科瑞和托庞嘉在帮我们办理入住手续，我在此欢迎你们来到太阳山滑雪旅馆，在这里可以让我们的思绪，远离那些私密关系，让我们之间的关系显露在外吧。
